{
  "title": "Rich Jamaican Beef Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and romantic Jamaican dish featuring mixed beef cuts in a yeasty and creamy sauce, served in a scallop shell, with a twist of pickle for added flavor, plant-based friendly by using vegan yeast and plant-based creamer.",
  "cuisine": "Jamaican",
