  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 300 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Season the beef with allspice and thyme.",
    "Brown the beef in a skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the onion and garlic to the skillet and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the pickle, vegan yeast, and plant-based creamer to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a Dutch oven and cover with a lid.",
    "Bake for 2 1/2 hours or until the beef is tender.",
    "Serve the stew in scallop shells and garnish with chopped fresh herbs if desired.",
    "Note: this recipe is for refrigerator pickling/preserving only — store in the refrigerator and consume within 1 week. Do not water-bath can without an acid (vinegar or lemon juice)."
